          {
            "title": "append()",
            "id": 79676,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para agregar el valor <code>25</code> a una lista, escribimos el nombre de la lista seguido de un punto <code>.</code>, luego la instrucción <code>append(25)</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"scores = [\" /><text value=\"24\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"23\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"scores.append(\" /><text value=\"25\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(scores)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"25\" endIndex=\"31\" /><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"32\" /><option startIndex=\"32\" endIndex=\"34\" /><option startIndex=\"34\" endIndex=\"35\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"[24, 23, 25]\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>append</code> seguido de <code>(</code> y luego <code>25</code>, <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "append()",
            "id": 79675,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Agregar un valor con <code>.append()</code> lo coloca al final de la lista. Podemos ver el resultado aquí codificando <code>print(users)</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"users = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;john&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;hannah&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;marco&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"users.append(\" /><text value=\"&quot;julian&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(users)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"59\" endIndex=\"64\" /><option startIndex=\"64\" endIndex=\"65\" /><option startIndex=\"65\" endIndex=\"70\" /><option startIndex=\"70\" endIndex=\"71\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"['john', 'hannah', 'marco', 'julian']\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>print</code> seguido de <code>(</code> y luego <code>users</code>, <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "insert()",
            "id": 79674,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Agregamos un valor a un índice específico con <code>insert()</code>. Al codificar <code>insert(0, \"lemon\")</code>, agregaremos el valor al inicio de la lista.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"shopping = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;kiwis&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;peas&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"shopping.insert(\" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;lemon&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(shopping)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"38\" endIndex=\"44\" /><option startIndex=\"44\" endIndex=\"56\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"['lemon', 'kiwis', 'peas']\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>insert</code> seguido de <code>(0, \"lemon\")</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Insert()",
            "id": 80441,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>La función <code>insert()</code> tiene dos parámetros. Primero, el índice donde queremos insertar el valor, seguido del valor.</p><p><code>insert(1, \"chocolate\")</code> añade un valor en la segunda posición.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"shopping = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;kiwis&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;peas&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"shopping.insert(\" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;lemon&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"shopping.insert(\" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;chocolate&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(shopping)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"66\" endIndex=\"72\" /><option startIndex=\"73\" endIndex=\"74\" /><option startIndex=\"74\" endIndex=\"75\" /><option startIndex=\"76\" endIndex=\"87\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"['lemon', 'chocolate', 'kiwis', 'peas']\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>insert</code> seguido de <code>1</code> y luego <code>,</code>, <code>\"chocolate\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
