            "title": "One at a time",
            "id": 79673,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para ambos <code>append()</code> e <code>insert()</code>, solo podemos agregar un elemento a la vez.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"initials = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;RM&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;LP&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"initials.append(\" /><text value=\"&quot;LC&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"initials.insert(\" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;LS&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(initials)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"33\" endIndex=\"39\" /><option startIndex=\"55\" endIndex=\"61\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"['RM', 'LS', 'LP', 'LC']\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>append</code> seguido de <code>insert</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "pop()",
            "id": 79672,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para eliminar el último elemento de una lista, escribimos el nombre de la lista <code>todo</code>, un punto <code>.</code>, y la instrucción <code>pop()</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"todo = [\" /><text value=\"&quot;call mom&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;dishes&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"]\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"todo.pop()\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(todo)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"35\" endIndex=\"40\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"['call mom']\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>pop()</code>.</p></body></html>"
